'''Francesco di Giovanni Botticini''' (1446 – 16 yennayer 1498), ar ittusemma s umata Francesco Botticini, ikka-t-inn iga yan umekla awṭalyan azayku n Tleslalit. Ilul-d ɣ Flurinsa iɣama-nn ar ikellu ar tamettant-nns ɣ 1498. Izzri wussan n  ulemmud-nns ammas n tsawriyen n [[Neri di Becci]], [[Cosimo Rosselli]] d [[Andrea del Verrocchio]]. Isersel-d tsawert-nns si-s iẓlin ammas n Flurinsa ḍart yat tizi ɣ iswurri zund umawas n Neri di Bicci's. Yat tkemmʷict n twuriwin ka ser-s itturruyen s usrid ɣ mayd izrin, macc' ufan-d inmezruyen ɣ yiseggʷasen-ad gguranin mennawt twuriwin-yaḍnin ser-s tetturruynin s tenẓi. zeɣ mayd ittusmutter record ummid n twuriwin-nns, yurri ar ittyawḥasb zund yan zeɣ yimeqranen n tẓuri n Tleslalit bahra ttyawɣḍafnin.

Tiwuriwin n Botticini akkʷ dar- tettyawssannin; d Tabernacle n Sacrament, Assumption n Tamgudt d Madonna d Urba deg Glory d Maryam Tagʷrramt Tawmejdaliyt d Bernard Agʷrram.

==Tudert nns==
Ilul-d Francesco Botticini aseggʷas n 1446 ɣ Flurinsa, meqqar d nit ur ittyawssan asakud ineɣden. Ibba-s, Giovanni di Domenico di Piero, ikka-t-inn iga awed netta amekla. S ufulki n contacts-nns nna iṭṭaf ammas n umaḍal n tẓuri akud-ann, yufa Francesco ad iswurri dar Neri di Bicci zund umawas-nns. Ibda ar as-ittawes ɣ tsawert-nns ijujjgen ass n 22 yulyu 1459 ddaw yat temɣunt (contrat) n yan useggʷas n usluɣmu. Tekka-tt-inn dar-s 13 useggʷas ɣ tizi-ann. S tmentilt n tegrumma n yinaẓuren dar tekka yat tmefkiyt taxatart ammas n tsawert-ann, yufa ufeddam n Botticini ad yili yan exposure igan azalan.

Meqqar dar-s tekka temɣunt n yan useggʷas, ifel Francesco tasawert n Bicci ɣ yulyuz 1460 ḍart tẓa wayyuren n usluɣmu ur d uggar. "Da ssefrun imassanen tasimant-nns tazaykut s trarit-nnsen n tmentilt i tezrirt n carrière n baba-s ɣ teklut d ula connections-nns d inaẓuren-yaḍnin". Nnan mas d lliɣ d-iffuɣ tsawert n Bricci, izzri ɣ tin [[Andrea del Verrocchio]] yan imikk, s tmuni n mennaw ɣ contemporaries-nns, seg-sen [[Leonardo Da Vinci|Leonardo da Vinci]], [[Lorenzo di Credi]], [[Domenico Ghirlandaio]], d [[Pietro Perugino]]. Is ka, ur illi kra n wanẓa ittuzemmamen immalen mas d nit iswurri ɣ tsawert n Verrocchio. ar ittyafa yan wanẓa igan usrid f wassaɣ-nnsen akud-ann ɣ "collaboration" n Francesco d Verrocchio ɣ itsent twuriwin, d tezrirt n tmamekt-nns nna ikkan f tfelwin n Francesco. Irwas is d-tekka tmentilt n uyad amḥizwer d yinaẓuren imafkayen yaḍnin ammas n tsawert, irẓem-d Botticini ɣ 1469 tasawert-nns si-s iẓlin, zun d imk-nna "reported" ɣ yan warra n "arbitration" mu ittuɣul usakud s useggʷas igan yan. Idum wassaɣ-nns n twuri d Verrocchio ar 1475 s mayd idrusen.

==Tiwuriwin-nns==
===Agiṭun n Sacrament===
[[Afaylu:Francesco Botticini Tabernacle of the Sacramento. Empoli Museum.jpg|thumb|''Agiṭun n Sacrament''|269x269px]]
Tettufka Agiṭun n Sacrament (Tabernacle n Sacrament) zund yat altarpiece (tafelwit ittilin ɣ isɣersen) i useɣres unnig n teglizt ammas n Empoli, Ṭṭalyan. ar tettɣama tad, tga yat zeɣ twuriwin n Botticini akkʷ tettwaɣḍafnint. Ittugna Andrew Agʷrram, nna igan agʷrram patron n teglizt akud-ann, f uzelmaḍ n usibiryum (Ciborium). f ufasi-nns, tigemmi n Eucharist; tella yat tfelwit n John Agʷrram Amseddam. Ddaw snat tugniwin-ad tireslalint, ilint kraḍt tfelwin meẓẓinint ɣ predella (tadabut f ar srusen id altarpiece). f uzelmaḍ, ittugna "Martyrdom" n Andrew Agʷrram ddaw-as s usrid. ar ittyafa Imensi Aneggaru ɣ tuẓẓumt d Martyrdom n ugʷrram John Amseddam ɣ "compartment" f ufasi; ddaw tfeliwt imeqquren n John Amseddam.

Ittuɣtes yad-lli ad temmed "altarpiece" ɣ 15 ɣuct 1486, is ka ur nit tettres ammas n teglizt ar 1491. Ur tettusmed twuri-nns ar 1504 llig tkellef taglizt iwi-s n Francesco Botticini, Raffaello, ad as-ikemmel tawuri s umsasa d temɣunt taneṣliyt.

===Turda n Temgudt d Igʷrramen d Umyellel Aneglusan===
[[Afaylu:Francesco Botticini - The Assumption of the Virgin.jpg|thumb|''Turda n Temgudt''|left|375x375px]]
Tga Turda n Temgudt (Assumption of the Virgin) tawuri n Francesco akkʷ ittyawssanen. Kkan-t-inn ɣ tezwiri ar ttraran tajmilt n usnulfu-nns i [[Sandro Botticelli]] f uyenna ibder Vasari ɣ udlis-nns "Tudert n Inaẓuren", maca ssenẓan inmezruyen n tẓuri ḍart wakud-ann mas d tawuri n Botticini ad tga. Iddem Botticini ɣ teklut-nns zikk n 1475, ismed-tt ɣ 1477 ḍart sin yiseggasen. Tɣey tfelwit ad tettayafa ɣassa ɣ Usefser Anamaur, London.

